description:
Brand New 2022 Sundowner 22 f oot Car Hauler with the race nose and spread axle set up. People go nuts when they see this trailer! Bring a pair of sunglasses because you will need them! Never worry about rust again!


If you're looking for the Best Aluminum car hauler in the country, Sundowner is the choice! Sundowner is well known for top quality race car trailers and live in style horse and livestock trailers. The quality of the build can be seen in these open style car haulers as well. Unlike some aluminum trailers on the market this trailer has no moving axle hardware such as springs, bushings. 



SIZE - 22 foot long, 82" wide between fenders. 

LOAD CAPACITY - 8050 LBS GVWR 

Spread Axle with Painted fenders. 

AXLES - 6 lug torsion 3500 lbs axles with E-Z lube hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels, required by CO law 

Safety breakaway kit as required by CO law. 

RAMPS - 8 foot Aluminum rear or side load 12 inch wide. 

TIRES - D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen Goodyear tire upgrade! 

HITCH - 2-5/16ths Bulldog 12,500 LBS Coupler, best you can buy! Most requested! 

TIE DOWNS - (4) Large swivel Stainless Steel 

WARRANTY - 8 Year Transferable 2 year bumper to hitch 

LIGHTS - LED 11 Marker lights and two tail lights Looks fantastic at night. 

ROCK Guard with Black Skin and spare mount - removable 

FENDERS - Removable and painted to match 

WIRING - Professional sealed harness 



Very well optioned and works smoothly. The aluminum frame is a 6 inch channel and tube main frame construction. Each of the floor planks are interlocking and are welded together creating a structured support every 6 inches. These have 6 foot aluminum ramps that can be used on the rear or the side of the trailer. This trailer has running boards that can also be used as steps and it has two removable teardrop fenders allowing you to open doors on cars and exit the vehicle and trailer with ease. This trailer also has 4 large swivel tie-downs. The tires are D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen mounted on custom aluminum 6 lug wheels. The axles are 3500 lbs torsion axles with E-Z lub hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels. This trailer is equipped with a breakaway safety kit and a 2 5/16's bulldog style hitch. All of the lights are LED. This trailer is available in different sizes and can be equipped with many optional features such as rock guards, storage boxes, spare tire mounts and more. 



This trailer is backed by an 8 year bumper to hitch transferable structural warranty. 



Financing is available with Sheffield Financial, Trailer Solutions Financial and Synchrony car car, WAC. In many cases these finance plans do not require down payments and have many great plans to choose from that fit many needs.

description:
PLEASE NOTE NEW LOCATION IS 1484 CR 27 BRIGHTON CO 80603 



ASK about Financing no interest for 3 months, no payments for 4 months WAC Financing. 



Brand New 2021 Sundowner 16, 18 and 20 foot All Purpose Trailers (AP 4000). 



People go nuts when they see this trailer! Bring a pair of sunglasses because you will need them! Never worry about rust again! These are great for hauling cars, equipment, Side by Sides and more.
If your looking for the Best Aluminum hauler in the country, Sundowner is the choice! Sundowner is well known for top quality race car trailers and live in style horse and livestock trailers. The quality of the build can be seen in these open style haulers as well. Unlike some aluminum trailers on the market this trailer has no moving axle hardware such as springs, or bushings they use torsion axles for life long quiet performance. 



SIZE - 16, 18 and 20 foot long, 82" wide between fenders. And the fenders come off. 

LOAD CAPACITY - 9200 LBS GVWR Read that again! 9200 pounds! 

AXLES - 6 lug torsion 4000 lbs axles with E-Z lube hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels, as required by CO law 

Safety breakaway kit also as required by CO law. 

RAMPS - 7 foot Aluminum rear or side load 12 inch wide. 

TIRES - D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen 

HITCH - 2-5/16's Bulldog 12,500 LBS Coupler, best you can buy! Most requested! 

TIE DOWNS - (6) Large swivel Stainless Steel 

WARRANTY - 8 Year Transferable structural, 3 year bumper to hitch warranty and one year tire and wheel replacement. 

LIGHTS - LED 11 Marker lights and two tail lights Looks fantastic at night. 

BUMP RAIL - 10 inch 

FENDERS - Removable and making an excellent car hauler trailer. 

WIRING - Professional sealed harness 

TOOL BOX - diamond plate lockable with a work / cargo light behind the box 

Very well optioned and works smoothly. The aluminum frame is a 6 inch channel and tube main frame construction. Each of the floor planks are interlocking and are welded together creating a structured support every 6 inches. These have 7 foot aluminum ramps that can be used on the rear or the side of the trailer.Two removable teardrop fenders allowing you to open doors on cars and exit the vehicle and trailer with ease. This trailer also has 6 large swivel tie-downs. The tires are D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen mounted on custom aluminum 6 lug wheels. The axles are 4000 lbs torsion axles with E-Z lub hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels. This trailer is equipped with a breakaway safety kit and a 2 5/16's bulldog style hitch. All of the lights are LED. This trailer is available in different sizes and can be equipped with many optional features such as rock guards, storage boxes, spare tire mounts and more.
This trailer is backed by an 3 year bumper to hitch warranty and an 8 year transferable structural warranty.
Financing is available with Sheffield Financial, Trailer Solutions Financial and Synchrony car car, WAC. In many cases these finance plans do not require down payments and have many great plans to choose from that fit many needs.
Pricing: Plus tax, ad prices include a 3% cash discount already applied. Other forms of payment such as sub prime finance, finance and credit cards may not qualify for the discount. 



All forms payments accepted. including paypal and Venmo 



16 Foot AP 4000 = 2021 As equipped, with custom wheels and D load radial tires Includes tool box, stk AP400016 8233 As equipped. spare included. 



18 Foot AP 4000 = With custom wheels and D load radial tires, Includes tool box stk AP400018 as quipped spare included. 



Ask about our line of tie downs for all your toys. (4) 6 foot 10K ratchet straps starting at 140.00 dollars per set
Offered by dealer, Schrecks Auto stk number AP400016, 18 and 20. Price is plus tax and DMV fees but we do not charge dealer handling fees. We accept all forms of payment but the advertised price does include a cash discount of 3%. Other forms of payment such as sub prime financing may not qualify for this discount.

description:
PLEASE NOTE NEW LOCATION IS 1484 CR 27 BRIGHTON CO 80603 



ASK about Financing 6 months same as cash or plans starting at 5.99% WAC Financing. 



Brand New 2022 Sundowner 16, 18 and 20 foot All Purpose Trailers (AP 4000). 



People go nuts when they see this trailer! Bring a pair of sunglasses because you will need them! Never worry about rust again! These are great for hauling cars, equipment, Side by Sides and more.
If you're looking for the Best Aluminum hauler in the country, Sundowner is the choice! Sundowner is well known for top quality race car trailers and live in style horse and livestock trailers. The quality of the build can be seen in these open style haulers as well. Unlike some aluminum trailers on the market this trailer has no moving axle hardware such as springs, or bushings they use torsion axles for life long quiet performance. 



SIZE - 16, 18 and 20 foot long, 82" wide between fenders. And the fenders come off. 

LOAD CAPACITY - 9200 LBS GVWR Read that again! 9200 pounds! 

AXLES - 6 lug torsion 4000 lbs axles with E-Z lube hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels, as required by CO law 

Safety breakaway kit also as required by CO law. 

RAMPS - 7 foot Aluminum rear or side load 12 inch wide. 

TIRES - D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen 

HITCH - 2-5/16's Bulldog 12,500 LBS Coupler, best you can buy! Most requested! 

TIE DOWNS - (6) Large swivel Stainless Steel 

WARRANTY - 8 Year Transferable structural, 3 year bumper to hitch warranty and one year tire and wheel replacement. 

LIGHTS - LED 11 Marker lights and two tail lights Looks fantastic at night. 

BUMP RAIL - 10 inch 

FENDERS - Removable and making an excellent car hauler trailer. 

WIRING - Professional sealed harness 

TOOL BOX - diamond plate lockable with a work / cargo light behind the box 

Very well optioned and works smoothly. The aluminum frame is a 6 inch channel and tube main frame construction. Each of the floor planks are interlocking and are welded together creating a structured support every 6 inches. These have 7 foot aluminum ramps that can be used on the rear or the side of the trailer. Two removable teardrop fenders allowing you to open doors on cars and exit the vehicle and trailer with ease. This trailer also has 6 large swivel tie-downs. The tires are D load radial 225/75/15 filled with Nitrogen mounted on custom aluminum 6 lug wheels. The axles are 4000 lbs torsion axles with E-Z lub hubs with electric brakes on all 4 wheels. This trailer is equipped with a breakaway safety kit and a 2 5/16's bulldog style hitch. All of the lights are LED. This trailer is available in different sizes and can be equipped with many optional features such as rock guards, storage boxes, spare tire mounts and more.
This trailer is backed by an 2 year bumper to hitch warranty and an 8 year transferable structural warranty.
Financing is available with Sheffield Financial, Trailer Solutions Financial and Synchrony car car, WAC. In many cases these finance plans do not require down payments and have many great plans to choose from that fit many needs.
Pricing: Plus tax, ad prices include a 3% cash discount already applied. Other forms of payment such as sub prime finance, finance and credit cards may not qualify for the discount. 



All forms payments accepted. including paypal and Venmo 



16 Foot AP 4000 = 2022 As equipped, with custom wheels and D load radial tires Includes tool box, stk AP400016 As equipped. spare included. 



18 Foot AP 4000 = With custom wheels and D load radial tires, Includes tool box stk AP400018 as quipped spare included. 



20 Foot AP 4000 = With custom wheels and D load radial tires, Includes tool box stk AP400020 as quipped spare included. Spare included. 



Ask about our line of tie downs for all your toys. (4) 6 foot 10K ratchet straps starting at 110.00 dollars per set
Offered by dealer, Schrecks Auto stk number AP400016, 18 and 20. Price is plus tax and DMV fees but we do not charge dealer handling fees. We accept all forms of payment but the advertised price does include a cash discount of 3%. Other forms of payment such as sub prime financing may not qualify for this discount.

description:
PLEASE NOTE NEW LOCATION IS 1484 CR 27 BRIGHTON CO 80603 



In stock now!! I have entire stacks selling in 4 hours, deposits encouraged.... Another stack just arrived, another stack is always on the way. This is my most popular trailer for people to come see. Brand new. Straight from the factory! 2022 18 foot car haulers, tandem axle, 7,000 lbs 4 brake car hauler with Written Factory FOREVER warranty. I am not aware of anyone else offering this kind of coverage. I am a Local Licensed and Bonded Colorado dealer. No hidden charges, no delivery fees, no dealer handling fees. Pay for it with your CAR CARE ONE card or apply for one and receive 6 months or even a year to pay for the trailer no interest financing WAC. Also have financing with Trailer Solutions Financial, and Synchrony Financial WAC 

Equipped as Colorado Law requires with 4 brakes and breakaway kit. Two, 3500Lbs Dexter E-Z lube axles, the kind that you just grease with a grease gun. Built with super strong bulldog style 7,000 lbs coupler. Built with steel diamond plate over the dove tail for added protection. Lights, chains, and stow away ramps included. Wood Deck with 2 foot steel dovetail. Some brands use wood on the dove area and in my opinion that is a poor choice, if you have broken and damaged cars that is the area they tend to rub or drag and wood just will not hold up. At least 82 inches between fenders. I PREP MY TRAILERS BEFORE SALE Pre-tested, extra grounds added for superior operation of lights, brakes and equipment. Pre-inspected, wheels torqued to specification. Title work guaranteed to you with clean clear Colorado title. Vin inspection completed when needed, no charge. My Forever warranty covers, frame, welds, lights, wires, couplers, jacks, ramps, lifetime for original owner. Axles, brakes, bearings and hubs have a 2 year Dexter warranty. Deductible may apply. Call for details. Everything above included in sale price plus tax unless sales price indicates otherwise. Other designs and special orders available. as shown by additional pictures. Steel deck version, typically in stock! Pictured below. Side steps with bright diamond plate, in stock! Pictured below. 20 foot version, comes with upgraded frame and 4 foot of steel on dovetail. In stock. Drop leg jack upgrades, Fender upgrades, heavier axles 5200 lbs, 7,000 lbs, custom wheels and radial tires, winch plates, LED lights, utility styles and more....custom order if you like. Call or Text me today! E-mail is welcome as well. I take trades on just about anything! Credit card, Cash, personal check! Lets make a deal! Schrecks Auto is a licensed and bonded LOCAL Colorado dealer, no scams, no asking for paypal money upfront, no delivery fees and meeting in a parking lot for a fly by night transaction that you may find with out of state scam artist, if the deal is too good to be true there may be a reason. I am a Member of Colorado Independent Auto Dealers Association! Look at the trailer before you buy. Factory has delivered more than 6000 trailers, and they provide Lifetime warranty on all welds, frame and couplers. STK number 18CHapr22. More than one in stock. Subject to prior sale. Re-order at same price when stock is depleted, no rain check required 2 to 3 week lead time when out of stock.

description:
This car is on pcarmarket.com for auction right now. This is the real deal, one owner private owned, and extremely
clean. Never been smoked in, impeccably maintained. Fresh tires, fresh fluid and filter change
and this car has an entire front clear bra on bumper, fenders, hood, mirrors,
top body above windshield and lower accents. And it looks amazing. Believe me you will sit and stare at the
beauty of this vehicle for hours.
Serious inquiries only, shown by appointment only please. We have clean and clear title, no accidents or
damage. Don't let this opportunity to
own a supercar pass you by.
This 2015 911 Twin Turbo Porsche offering superior super car
performance and luxury accommodations no matter where life is taking you. The best description I have heard for this
car was "like a surgeon's scalpel" And its accurate. This car makes it easy to position yourself into
any given location you desire in the roadway with amazing precision. You may feel like you are the expert when you
are driving this super car because it gives you the confidence of a seasoned
race driver. But behind the scenes you are cutting through traffic with the
confidence of the All-Wheel Drive, while paddle shifting the 7 Speed
Doppelkuppiung (PDK) transmission, connected your 3.8 liter with 520 horsepower
and 487 foot pounds of torque, wrapped up in a perfectly balanced platform. Rear Axle Steering, Porsche active stability
Management system (PSM) with Antilock brakes (ABS) and Automatic Brake
differential (ABD) Anti-Slip Regulation (ASR) and Porsche Torque Vectoring Plus
(PTV Plus) Add all of this together and
you can still out perform even the best drivers while drinking your latte and
getting a quick kiss from your passenger that is leaning over the low-profile
center console.
If you do happen to mis-step, you will be comforted to know
you have eight airbags, Porsche Side Impact Protection system with even more
airbags built into the seats, side doors and seatbelt pre-tensioners and force
limiters.
Comfort features include Satellite stereo, Bluetooth hands
free, navigation, performance recording, Nav Weather, HD radio, 7 inch color
touch screen, and 18 way power seats wrapped in full leather.
Optioned with Black Paint, Luxor Beige interior, heated
seats, sport design mirrors, luggage nets, Sport Chrono package, electric slide
sunroof and tilt (glass top), Power steering plus, two tone leather package,
painted aluminum pedals, adaptive 18 way power seats, premium package plus,
Burmester High End Infotainment system, Black wheels, Bi-Zenon headlights, 20 inch wheels, sprot seats with
leather backrest shells, Low profile center console, and the ornamental Porsche
Crest.


Offered by dealer, Schrecks Auto, Price plus tax, NO dealer fees, advertised price includes a cash discount.
